# ffmpeg for Python

[![CI/CD](https://github.com/MatteoH2O1999/ffmpeg-binaries/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/MatteoH2O1999/ffmpeg-binaries/actions/workflows/ci.yml)
